    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1770713444\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于游戏。</strong></h2><br>100只狗 - 游戏的目标是找到狗！游戏有多个关卡和各种音乐伴奏，不会让你感到无聊。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/9b2119cb3bf6e9b59bbf69f3c7f6699e.poster.avif?t=1770713444\" width=518 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/9b2119cb3bf6e9b59bbf69f3c7f6699e.webm?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/9b2119cb3bf6e9b59bbf69f3c7f6699e.mp4?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有人会说 - “这很简单”。</strong></h2><br>认为一切都很简单？有些狗藏得非常好，所以如果你在没有提示的情况下完成所有关卡，那将是令人惊讶的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/5a9dd38b0cb7fbe5c011bc3a1983a343.poster.avif?t=1770713444\" width=518 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/5a9dd38b0cb7fbe5c011bc3a1983a343.webm?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/5a9dd38b0cb7fbe5c011bc3a1983a343.mp4?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关卡。</strong></h2><br>穿越充满惊喜和谜题的巧妙隐藏关卡迷宫。探索各种各样的地方 - 从繁忙的城市街道到神秘的森林和废弃的遗址。每个新地点都会带来意想不到的挑战，还有更多。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>城市<br></li><li>西部<br></li><li>日本<br></li><li>等等</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/8032b6247c7e7134d607e940758a46ba.poster.avif?t=1770713444\" width=518 height=518 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/8032b6247c7e7134d607e940758a46ba.webm?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/8032b6247c7e7134d607e940758a46ba.mp4?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1770713444\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3048670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1770713444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
